data.description: Welcoming 4 bed 3 bath home with expansive 3-car garage on quiet street. The updated kitchen has brand new stainless steel appliances, granite counters, ceramic backsplash, gleaming hardwood floors and pantry.  It leads to a large cedar deck that walks down to concrete patio area. The owner's suite includes private full bath with dual vanities and a spacious walk-in closet.  The sizable family room is highlighted by a beautiful full built-in entertainment center. Conveniently located  within a mile of the high school and Target.  It is scheduled to get new siding and roof. If you buy it soon, you can pick the colors. Don't miss this great opportunity!
